In [15]:
targetSite = 'https://www.starbucks.co.kr/store/getStore.do?r=A2QIBZBBIG'
request = requests.post(targetSite, data ={
    'p_sido_cd' : '01',                
    'p_gugun_cd' : '0101',                 
    'ins_lat' : '37.3707697',          
    'ins_lng' : '127.0078127',         
    'in_biz_cd' : '',
    'iend' : 2000,                     
    'set_date' : ''
    
})
star_json = json .loads(request.text)
star_df = json_normalize(star_json, 'list')
star_df_map = star_df[['s_name','sido_code','sido_name','gugun_code','gugun_name','doro_address','lat','lot']]
star_df_map['lat'] = star_df_map['lat'].astype(float)
star_df_map['lot'] = star_df_map['lot'].astype(float)

star_map = folium.Map(location = [star_df_map['lat'].mean(),star_df_map['lot'].mean()], zoom_start = 14)

for index, star in star_df_map.iterrows():
    popup = folium.Popup(star['s_name']+',  : ' + star['doro_address'], max_width = 600) 
    folium.Marker(location = [star['lat'], star['lot']], popup = popup).add_to(star_map)
star_map

In [17]:
targetSite = 'https://www.starbucks.co.kr/store/getStore.do?r=A2QIBZBBIG'
request = requests.post(targetSite, data ={
    'p_sido_cd' : '08',                
    'p_gugun_cd' : '0826',                 
    'ins_lat' : '37.3707697',          
    'ins_lng' : '127.0078127',         
    'in_biz_cd' : '',
    'iend' : 2000,                     
    'set_date' : ''
    
})
star_json = json .loads(request.text)
star_df = json_normalize(star_json, 'list')
star_df_map = star_df[['s_name','sido_code','sido_name','gugun_code','gugun_name','doro_address','lat','lot']]
star_df_map['lat'] = star_df_map['lat'].astype(float)
star_df_map['lot'] = star_df_map['lot'].astype(float)

star_map = folium.Map(location = [star_df_map['lat'].mean(),star_df_map['lot'].mean()],tiles='Stamen Toner', zoom_start = 12)

for index, star in star_df_map.iterrows():
    popup = folium.Popup(star['s_name']+',  : ' + star['doro_address'], max_width = 600) 
    folium.CircleMarker(
        location = [star['lat'], star['lot']],
        popup = popup,
        radius=7,
        opacity = 0.7,
        color='#0B610B',
        fill_color='#0B6121'
    ).add_to(star_map)
    
star_map
